9c55c1b","tid":909440,"uid":157193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"597049e127b3eacc982a8521c45834e954da19f9","tid":909440,"uid":9053,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T11:33:48.000Z","msg":"如果係日本，就食納豆，記得要加水煲成納豆沙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T11:48:25.000Z","msg":"見到你咁講 試左一試<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想講一聲 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 係日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d7f8a0996f3f7ec33e36a6a275b7bd9e160f45","tid":909440,"uid":2756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T11:49:05.000Z","msg":"卡路士"},{"pid":"2b1b7ee24ef7925ddb9e7a165dbba9a001852d9e","tid":909440,"uid":2033,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T11:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/151621_0987b0284c945ddef95ff8f3d3e31f87.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F151621_0987b0284c945ddef95ff8f3d3e31f87.gif&h=f6c8c49c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"085f71f98f0bb272bd49eb1a16827bd27a7f8347","tid":909440,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T11:52:27.000Z","msg":"咪撚講啦"},{"pid":"9ea38c75985d54f953fa47651a6fd11d615b7d29","tid":909440,"uid":49269,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T11:56:00.000Z","msg":"巴打你好<br />\n<br />\n想當日我亦曾經有過同一個疑問<br />\n<br />\n無知的我向各位集思廣益<br />\n<br />\n一問之下反應奇好<br />\n<br />\n正當我諗住逐一試既時候<br />\n<br />\n有人同我講綠豆 實火先清<br />\n<br />\n我當堂高興得夢遺<br />\n<br />\n點解??<br />\n<br />\n因為我想像唔到原來有咁簡單既方法<br />\n<br />\n我漏夜買左一公斤綠豆諗住夠我清一年熱氣<br />\n<br />\n因為唔清楚份量  追問每次要食幾多粒 一日幾多次之後<br />\n<br />\n有條茂利竟然話&quot;煲水呀你老味,通屋奇應丸咩?&quot;<br />\n<br />\n我當堂就嚇一條   然後就得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n世間上竟然有啲咁無知既人<br />\n<br />\n所以我到而家都仲每日向天父祈求<br />\n<br />\n希望天主可以令世界再無弱智人士<br />\n<br />\n然而,有與我當日有一樣疑問的你<br />\n<br />\n來吧, 我以過來人身份願意教你響外國清熱氣<br />\n<br />\n儘管來,不要怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌晒你地老母"}]}